'''焦磷酸测序'''（{{lang-en|Pyrosequencing}}）是一种基于[[聚合酶链反应|聚合酶链反应]]原理的[[DNA测序|DNA测序]]（确定DNA中[[核苷酸|核苷酸]] 的顺序）方法。它与[[桑格法|桑格法]]不同，依赖于核苷酸掺入中[[焦磷酸盐|焦磷酸盐]]的释放，而非[[双脱氧核苷三磷酸|双脱氧核苷三磷酸]]参与的链终止反应。<ref>{{cite web|title=Definition of pyrosequencing from the Nature Reviews Genetics Glossary|url=http://www.nature.com/nrg/journal/v6/n11/glossary/nrg1709_glossary.html|accessdate=2008-10-28|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/66YeoBZHy?url=http://www.nature.com/nrg/journal/v6/n11/glossary/nrg1709_glossary.html|archive-date=2012-03-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>该技术是由{{le|穆斯塔法·罗纳吉|Mostafa Ronaghi}}和{{le|波尔·尼伦|Pål Nyrén}}于1996年在斯德哥尔摩的[[皇家工学院|皇家工学院]]发展出来的。<ref name=RonachiScience>{{Cite journal|title=A Sequencing Method Based on Real-Time Pyrophosphate|url=https://www.science.org/doi/10.1126/science.281.5375.363|last=Ronaghi|first=Mostafa|last2=Uhlén|first2=Mathias|date=1998-07-17|journal=Science|issue=5375|doi=10.1126/science.281.5375.363|volume=281|pages=363–365|language=en|pmid=9705713|issn=0036-8075|last3=Nyrén|first3=Pål|access-date=2021-11-10|archive-date=2021-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211110122310/https://www.science.org/doi/10.1126/science.281.5375.363|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Real-time DNA sequencing using detection of pyrophosphate release|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/8923969|last=Ronaghi|first=M.|last2=Karamohamed|first2=S.|date=1996-11-01|journal=Analytical Biochemistry|issue=1|doi=10.1006/abio.1996.0432|volume=242|pages=84–89|issn=0003-2697|pmid=8923969|last3=Pettersson|first3=B.|last4=Uhlén|first4=M.|last5=Nyrén|first5=P.|access-date=2021-11-10|archive-date=2021-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211019202001/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/8923969/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=The history of pyrosequencing|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/17185753|last=Nyrén|first=Pål|date=2007|journal=Methods in Molecular Biology (Clifton, N.J.)|doi=10.1385/1-59745-377-3:1|volume=373|pages=1–14|issn=1064-3745|pmid=17185753|access-date=2021-11-10|archive-date=2021-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211110151831/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/17185753/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

